{"tid":186609,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選舉處「失腦」花500萬寄信道歉","createTime":"2017-04-04T10:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T22:50:44.000Z","uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"777dce74dc7aa264703aa8eed2ea589dab58c7a6","tid":186609,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:28:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">哇! 唔講唔知我收到個封電郵值萬幾蚊一封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定還是政府向每個選民派錢補償我未收到通知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】選舉事務處在特首選舉期間，於後備會場亞洲博覽館遺失兩部載有全港選民資料的電腦。處方昨日首度解釋，指攜帶全港選民資料到會場，是要核實一千一百九十四名選委身分，事後檢討亦認為不適宜，又承認當時沒有人在會場看守電腦。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">處方於事後發信向全港選民道歉，共花了五百多萬公帑。</span></strong><br />\n　　總選舉事務主任黃思文解釋，選舉事務處設立了一套選民資料查詢系統，透過輸入身分證號碼核實選民資格。在各級選舉中，系統可供羈留人士於警署投票時，以身分證核對選民身分，亦會在特首選舉時核實選委資料。處方經初步檢視，基於不同選民基礎，認為有關系統不適宜應用於特首選舉中。<br />\n　　新民黨田北辰批評，「搲穿頭」都不明白<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>三百多萬名選民</strong></span>的資料與特首選委有何關係。黃思文稱：「以前都試過有一些不是選委，但又入了場，同事會靠這個系統核實。」田北辰即駁斥：「不是選委便不是選委，為何要解釋？請他離開囉。」<br />\n　　民主黨林卓廷質疑有沒有保安看管兩部電腦，黃思文指，會根據政府的保安規例辦事，他在追問下並承認，電腦在完成測試後放置在上鎖的儲物室，其後沒有人在場看管電腦，直至選舉翌日才揭發失竊事件。申訴專員劉燕卿表示正跟進遺失電腦事件，審視當中是否牽涉行政失當，會視乎事件是否牽涉廣大公眾利益，再決定是否作出主動調查。<br />\n　　另外，政制及內地事務局局長譚志源指，青年新政兩名前立法會議員梁頌恆和游蕙禎的案件，仍要在終審法院處理，在所有司法程序完結後，選管會才會決定補選日期。他指，政府已預留三點二億元作立法會補選之用，其中梁游議席補選的選區預計需約一點五億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E8%99%95-%E5%A4%B1%E8%85%A6-%E8%8A%B1500%E8%90%AC%E5%AF%84%E4%BF%A1%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89-221113194.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%2599%2595-%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%2585%25A6-%25E8%258A%25B1500%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25AF%2584%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AD%2589-221113194.html&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=86077b9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E8%99%95-%E5%A4%B1%E8%85%A6-%E8%8A%B1500%E8%90%AC%E5%AF%84%E4%BF%A1%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89-221113194.html</a>"},{"pid":"c098208e37a24cc3db7099edd1798b3af6a57f20","tid":186609,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"痴撚線政府"},{"pid":"b7c0042c233f989a117f47aa9d86e07a2c22d0ac","tid":186609,"uid":16041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:35:44.000Z","msg":"500萬/3百幾萬 = 萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b12aa93924b1297b4d91e3d1a5ca0402594652c","tid":186609,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:38:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>500萬/3百幾萬 = 萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non9左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蚊幾一封都過分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ffd83ca94e0976e6add29d577ea7fa53ebddf4","tid":186609,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>500萬/3百幾萬 = 萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n秒 <img src=\"/assets/fac